parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel Tank Overflow/Fuel Check Valve Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel check valve can cause the fuel tank to overflow, leading to a fire hazard, damage to the vehicle's body, and potential harm to the driver and passengers.
symptoms: Fuel spills out of the filler neck when refueling
fuel pump clicks off but fuel continues to flow
fuel overflows even when the tank is not full
rust forms on the vehicle's body near the fuel tank
and fuel spills on the driver and surrounding area.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel Tank Overflow/Fuel Inlet Check Valve Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel inlet check valve can cause fuel to overflow from the tank, resulting in a fire hazard, pollution, and damage to the vehicle and surrounding property.
symptoms: Fuel erupts from the fuel filler neck when the tank is full
fuel spills out of the tank during refueling
the pump shuts off and then fuel spews out
fuel overflows onto the vehicle and ground
fuel leaks from the filler tube inlet check valve
and rusting in the area where the fuel spill occurs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injury or death in the event of a crash, as the airbags may not deploy properly or at all.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag system fails to deploy in a crash
the airbag system deploys unexpectedly
or the airbag system is inoperable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The Takata airbag recall has led to a shortage of replacement parts, causing delays and inconveniences for vehicle owners, and potentially putting them at risk due to the faulty airbag system.
symptoms: Difficulty scheduling a recall repair
lack of availability of replacement parts
long wait times for repairs
and frustration with the recall process.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vehicle stalling can cause accidents, especially if it occurs while driving at high speeds or in heavy traffic.
symptoms: The vehicle shuts off without warning
no warning lights or indicators
and loss of power steering and brakes when the vehicle stalls.
